&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Innovecs &lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Innovecs is a global digital transformation and product development company. We partner with Fortune 500 and mid-market organizations to deliver &lt;strong&gt;custom software development, digital transformation, and technology services&lt;/strong&gt; that accelerate growth and optimize operations. With delivery centers across the globe, our teams bring deep domain expertise in &lt;strong&gt;Supply Chain &amp;amp; Logistics.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Innovecs, we foster a culture built on&lt;strong&gt; innovation, transparency, and collaboration.&lt;/strong&gt; We empower our people to thrive, and we deliver measurable business outcomes for our clients worldwide.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
