&lt;p data-start=&quot;657&quot; data-end=&quot;984&quot;&gt;The position emphasizes expanding existing client partnerships and creating new opportunities from established networks, rather than generating leads from scratch. Success in this role is driven by the ability to translate industry relationships into high-value IT services engagements and deliver measurable commercial impact.&lt;/p&gt;
